Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 博士 小心\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doctor! Doctor, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他去哪了 看见他了吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Where's he gone? Do you see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那 停下 不\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There he is. Stop! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,小心\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在那儿 那儿\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,它就是这样吼叫起来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's what it did, it went...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.08,0:01:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你认为那是我人生中最刺激的一天\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And if you think that was the most exciting day of my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,等听完其余的再说吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}wait till you hear the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 天哪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在那 和那个吼叫的东西一起\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So there I was, with that thing going...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 好孩子 吃东西 过来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Here, boy. Eat the food. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看看这可爱的食物 是不是很棒 非常棒\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Look at the lovely food, isn't that nice? Isn't it? Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,离开这里 快点\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Get out of here, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真乖 谁想吃猪排骨\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's a boy! Who'd like a porky choppy, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我说"跑"\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I said run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,错了 你真是越帮越忙\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Wrong one! You made it worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你说"蓝的"\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You said blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我说"不要蓝的"\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I said not blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我见过你吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Don't I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本无法想像 博士的机器\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You can't imagine it, the Doctor's machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上最美妙的声音\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The most beautiful sound in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我第一次见到博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That wasn't the first time I met the Doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,当然也不是最后一次\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and it certainly wasn't the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 不\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这是个很棒的开场 我才放在开头\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I just put that bit at the beginning because it's a brilliant opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个关于我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But this is the story of me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,和我与外星人相遇的故事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and my encounters with alien life forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,事先警告一下\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But be warned!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它会越来越恐怖\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Because it is gonna get scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能需要一个遥控\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I need a remote control zoom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我只能身体前倾来操作 恐…怖\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm having to do that with a lean, the scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但不用担心\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But don't worry
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因为不会只有我坐在这儿讲话 哦不\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'cause it's not just me sitting here talking. Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着相机的是厄什拉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's Ursula on camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我的好朋友 厄什拉·布雷克\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}My good friend Ursula Blake
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着我全新的摄像机\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}on my brand-new camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那里以前是我家 就在那儿\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That was my family home, down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽力了 但现在有两个女人住着\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I did try but there's two women live there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她们不太友好\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}They're a bit severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但那是一切开始的地方\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But that is where it all started
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那是我第一次见到博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'cause that's when I first met the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,让我想想 我应该是三四岁大\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What was it? I must've been three or four years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,午夜 我走下楼\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Middle of the night I went downstairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这个男人就站在那\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and there was this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔顿 告诉我 他为什么会在那里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Elton? Tell me, why was he there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:04:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我到现在都不知道\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I still don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那是好多年前的事了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}All those years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 先说要事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Okay, first things first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫埃尔顿 不要和某位歌手弄混了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}My name is Elton, not to be confused with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我离开学校 找了份工作\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I left school, I got a job,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,在瑞塔后勤公司当运输经理\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}transport manager at Rita Logistics,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,普通小运输公司\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}modest little haulage company,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,十分普通的生活 然后…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}perfectly normal life, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都变得疯狂\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}it all went mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,两年前 我在镇上\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Two years ago I was in town,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在备货 没什么特别的 都是些普通东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I was stocking up, you know, nothing special, all the usual stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,突然\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}When all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,商店窗口里的假人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Shop-window dummies
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然活了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}come to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我活下来了 显然\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I survived, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,十二个月之后 我重回小镇\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Twelve months later, I'm back in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,想买套新衣服 好好买件像样的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm up West looking for a new suit,something nice and smart,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这时突然有一架飞行器从头顶飞过\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}when I hear this plane overhead...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但这还没完\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But it wasn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因为之后 圣诞节\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'Cause then, Christmas Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我在床上熟睡 甜美而安逸 早上七点多\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm in bed, fast asleep, nice and cosy,7:45 in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,突然之间…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}when all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我被困在床上\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And I'm stuck in bed, all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为地上到处是玻璃碎片\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'cause there's glass everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而我光着脚\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and I was barefoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我得制作一个简陋的的滑轮系统\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I had to invent this rudimentary pulley system
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好把我的鞋子吊上来 当我弄完时…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}just to reach my boots, and by the time I'd done that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是一切的开始\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And that's when it all started happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是这么认识厄什拉的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's how I met Ursula.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}His name is the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,也这样认识了维克多·肯尼迪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's how I met Victor Kennedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个蠢货\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You stupid man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,还这么认识了杰琪·泰勒\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's how I met Jackie Tyler.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,姓埃尔顿的人可不常见\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You don't meet many Eltons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,也是因为这样 我终于见到了博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And that's how I finally met the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,并发现了真相\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And realised the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我得说\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I should say
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我生活的全部\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}this isn't, you know, my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,并非都是太空船之类的东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's not all spaceships and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我喜欢很多东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'Cause I'm into all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢足球\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I like football.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢喝酒 喜欢西班牙\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I like a drink. I like Spain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要说一样我真的非常爱的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And if there's one thing I really, really love,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是杰夫·林恩和电光乐队\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}then it's Jeff Lynne and the Electric Light Orchestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你根本抵挡不住他们的魅力\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'Cause you can't beat a bit of ELO.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ The sun is shining in the sky ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:08:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ There ain't a cloud in sight ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ It's stopped raining ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ Everybody's in the play ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ And don't you know it's a beautiful day ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ Hey hey hey… ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,巨大的太空船漂浮在伦敦上空\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}great big spaceship hanging over London,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,想像一下吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}imagine the theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因特网彻底崩溃\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The internet went into meltdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但我继续深挖\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But I kept on digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有事情还在发生\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Something was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,某天在某个不起眼的博客里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And then one day, on some obscure little blog
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,博主叫厄什拉·布雷克\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}by someone called Ursula Blake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那是怎样的几率\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It was, like, chance in a million.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是他 又是那个男人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It was him, it was that man again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但照片是新的 在圣诞节拍的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But the photo was new. It was taken on Christmas Day,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但圣诞节刚刚过去\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}but Christmas just gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,而他看起来还和原来一样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and he looked exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}His name is the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什么博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doctor what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,人们都只知道这一点\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's all anyone knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在圣诞节那天 我在外面到处拍照\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}At Christmas Day, I was taking photos all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我都快被那些事情搞疯了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I went mad with it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,太空船 激光等等一切事情\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}spaceships and lasers and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们那晚都去了特拉法加广场\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We all went to Trafalgar Square that night
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为每个人都在欢庆自己能活下来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'cause everyone was celebrating just being alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我在他经过时拍了照片\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and I snapped him in passing, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一个普通男子\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}He was just some bloke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时没意识到他很重要\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I didn't realise he was significant
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,直到后来斯金纳先生告诉了我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}until Mr Skinner pointed it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是斯金纳先生\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Who's Mr Skinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 是我们一群人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, there's a few of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密圣所 都在研究这个博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The inner sanctum. All studying this Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我见过他 博士 我发誓\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I've seen him, the Doctor, I swear to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我小时候见过他\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I saw him when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他在我家里 就在楼下\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}He was in my house and he was downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别告诉我他看起来和现在一模一样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Don't tell me, he looked exactly the same then as he does now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 老天 你相信我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, my God, you believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我怎么认识厄什拉的 多亏了博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So that's how I met Ursula. All thanks to the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,结果发现我们都看了相同的网站\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Turns out we read all the same sites
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,而且她离我住的地方只有半英里路\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and she only lived half a mile away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她是一个很好的伙伴 可怜的厄什拉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She was like a proper mate. Poor Ursula.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但如她所说\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But like she said,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个小团体\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}there was this little community,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,人数很少\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}the select few,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的故事都和博士有关\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}all with their stories of the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这个小群体经常碰面\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}This little gang used to meet up
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,通常在麦考提街的老图书馆下面\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}underneath the old library on Maccateer Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,斯金纳先生姓科林 但我们总叫他斯金纳先生\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Mr Skinner, first name Colin, but we always called him Mr Skinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道为什么 只是这样叫\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I don't know why, we just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对我而言 博士不是一个人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}...to me, the Doctor isn't a man,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他更是一个原型的集合\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}he's more a collection of archetypes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.77,0:10:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是布里吉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Then there was Bridget.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这些不同的博士来来去去\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}...all these different Doctors come and go,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但唯一的不变的特征是这个假的警亭\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}but the single constant factor is this faux police box.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,它突然出现 贯穿所有的故事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It keeps cropping up throughout history.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她住在北边\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She lived way up north,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她从大老远赶过来 从不错过会议\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}but she travelled down without fail just for the meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来是布丽斯\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Then there was Bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我要做的是\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What I'm trying to do
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,总结博士对我们来说意味着什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}is sum up the Doctor. What he means to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她曾经多么甜美 布丽斯\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She was ever so sweet, Bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"保佑布丽斯" 我们经常这样说\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Bless Bliss, we used to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他能够象征什么 以及他应该象征什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What he could represent and what he should represent
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还有他\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and what he
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不会象征的某种事情\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}never won't represent sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该起个名字\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We should have a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 作为一个小组\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You know, as a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,名字是很重要的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Names are very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要的是一个强有力的名字\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What we need is a good, strong name,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,像一个团队 比如…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}like a team. Something like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦调查和侦探事务所\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}London Investigation 'N' Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,简称LINDA\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}LINDA for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你再说一次\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Say it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦调查和侦探事务所\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}London Investigation 'N' Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么是"N"\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}"N"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼 & 薯条\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Fish 'n' chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,摇 & 滚\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Rock 'n' roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,恰克·迪莫斯 & 布莱尔\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Chaka Demus 'n' Pliers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,LINDA 我喜欢 它不会太严肃\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Ah! LINDA, I like it. It's not too solemn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢"N"\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I like the 'N'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是LINDA的男人  - 还有女人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We're the men from LINDA. And the women.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,LINDA 联合组织\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}LINDA united.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你当场想到的吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Did you think of that on the spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我早就想用这个了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, I've wanted to use it for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,敬一杯LINDA\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I give you LINDA.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,LINDA\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}LINDA!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们每周都见面\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So we'd all meet up every week
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会谈点博士的东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and we'd talk about the Doctor for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不久后 布里吉开始弄吃的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But after a while, Bridget started cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天哪 真是太棒了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, my God, that's gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不 真的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, really. Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,其余的人 缩手\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The rest of you, get your hands off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来斯金纳先生会开始读书\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Next thing you know, Mr Skinner started his readings,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他自己撰写小说\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'cause he was writing his own novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最后一次你坐魔鬼列车\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}"That's the last time you ride the Ghost Train,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,琼尼·弗兰斯塔 现在祈祷吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}johnny Franzetta. "Now say your prayers!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,待续\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}To be continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,随着时间流逝 我们越来越了解对方\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Time went on. We got to know each other better and better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在我女儿失踪后 我开始加入这个组织\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I only started all this because my daughter disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但不是外星人把她带走\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But it wasn't aliens that took her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,而是毒品\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It was just drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我每周都来伦敦 为了找她\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I come down to London every week and I just keep looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 布里吉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, Bridget.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ I gave my love a chicken ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ It had no bone ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ I gave my love a cherry ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ It had no stone… ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ I've got a brand new pair of roller-skates ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ You've got a brand-new key… ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,后来发现布里吉竟然会弹钢琴\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Then it turned out that Bridget could play the piano,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我也说出了我对电光乐队的爱好\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and I confessed my love of ELO.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来你也能猜到 LINDA乐队\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Next thing you know, musical LINDA.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ You got me running going out of my mind ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ You got me thinking that I'm wasting my time ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ Don't bring me down… ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只是好玩而已\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}just for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ Don't bring me down…♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,该你了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Your go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,该你了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 别被电线绊倒了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Now, careful. Mind the cables
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,然后一切都改变了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And that's when it all changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在三月的一个周二晚上\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That Tuesday night in March.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他来了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's when he arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,亮灯\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那天我们遇见了维克多·肯尼迪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's when we met Victor Kennedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的黄金时代 结束了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And the golden age was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们终于见面了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So, we meet at last,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,LINDA\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}LINDA.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你 先生\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Pleased to meet you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 音乐太大声了吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm sorry, was the music too loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不 我不握手\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, no, no. I don't shake hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,后退后退 我饱受皮肤病折磨\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Back, back. I suffer from a skin complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,翅疹  - 噢 你是说湿疹\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Eczeema. Oh, you mean eczema.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这更糟 非常糟 我被碰到就会有水疱\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, this is worse, much worse. I blister to the touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,退后退后 你们都离远点 远点\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Back, back, all of you, further, further.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 别介意我问问 你是谁\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Sorry, don't mind me asking, but who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们你们的救星\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I am your salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是他\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's really him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你们忘了最初的目的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Forgotten your purpose in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们沉醉于乐队 蛋糕 那些乱七八糟的东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You, with your band and your cakes and your blubbing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,而他一直还在外面\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and all the while he still exists,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看 快看\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Look at him. just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,向后退 你们都往后退\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Move back, move back, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,等一会 注意这里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Hold on, wait for this bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,图像被切断了 但声音在继续\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The picture cuts out, but the sound still continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.77,0:15:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,听吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,听一听宇宙的声音\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Listen to the sound of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么 怎么了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What is it? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,别管他\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Leave him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前听到过 对吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You've heard it before, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候 在哪 你当时在哪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}When was it? Where? Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘记了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'd forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,直到现在\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是那个晚上\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But it was that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哪晚\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What night?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是个孩子\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I was just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我下楼的原因\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's why I went downstairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,它把我吵醒了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}it woke me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那个声音\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但那是什么声音\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.47,0:16:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么意思\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他飞船的声音\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That is the sound of his spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 开始作业\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Right then, homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,使用火炬木文件\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Using the Torchwood files,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以用全新视角来看这些旧数据\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}we're able to look at all the old databases in a completely new light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以勾画出博士更详细的轮廓\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We're able to build up a more detailed profile of the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经给你们每个人分配任务\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I've allocated tasks to each of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你们…小心 注意痴疹\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'd like you to... Careful, watch the eczeema.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你们能完成这些目标\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I would like you to complete your targets
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,下周这个时候我们再在这里见面\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and meet back here this time next week,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,离抓住博士更近一步了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}one step closer to catching the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要只坐在这 行动起来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Well, don't just sit there! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,布丽斯 是布丽斯 对吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Um, Bliss? It is Bliss, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yea h. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,请问可以和你私下聊几句吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Could I have a word with you in private, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Course you can, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,再见  - 再见\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Goodbye, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,最好开始工作\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Better get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多事要做\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Lots to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没把它当成工作\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I never thought of it as work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这是我们一直想要的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's what we've always wanted, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,找到博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}To find the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:16:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我想是的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yeah, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,突然 任何人都没说一句话\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}All of a sudden, without anyone saying so,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都开始为维克多·肯尼迪工作\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}we were working for Victor Kennedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们得承认\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But we had to admit,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他是对的 他的方法精确严格\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}he was right. His methods were much more rigorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉我们离博士越来越近\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It' felt like we were getting closer and closer to the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,肯尼迪先生\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Mr Kennedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想知道…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We were wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,布丽斯不见了 你知道她在哪吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No sign of Bliss. Do you know where she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 她没告诉你们吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yes. Didn't she tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她结婚了 她留了信息\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She's getting married. She left a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不会长久的 蠢女孩\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It'll never last. Stupid girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 继续工作\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Come on, back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但有次我们很幸运\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But we did get lucky once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一个刚到的警亭…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}A police box, newly arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,上面说到今天才刚到伍尔维奇\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It says newly arrived today. It's in Woolwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不要光站在那 行动 行动 走走\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Well, don't just stand there! Move! Move! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但别太激动 接下来就是刚开始那段\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But don't get excited. That's where you came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,伍尔维奇 警亭 红水桶 蓝水桶\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Woolwich, police box, red bucket, blue bucket,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,笨拙的我 等等…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}me so stupid, etcetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没用的东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我被吓呆了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I just froze.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你见到了他 你却呆住了 蠢货\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You met him and you froze? You stupid man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能打我 你不能碰我 你有皮肤病\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You can't hit me 'cause you don't touch. You get a rash and an itch and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我就用这个\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I can use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢用那手杖打他的话 你会被我臭骂一顿\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Use that cane on him and you'll get one hell of a smack off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,然后再一顿猛踢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And then a good kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白了吗 肯尼迪先生\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Is that completely understood, Mr Kennedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,非常明白\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Duly noted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,厄什拉·布雷克\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Ursula Blake,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,最具有反抗的可能性\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}most likely to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 我们要改变方向\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Right then, we'll change tack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从侧向着手\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We'll approach this sideways.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们想探究博士的真相\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}If we're to discover the truth about the Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我们应该找到…她\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}then we need to try and find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,每当涉及到博士的伙伴\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Now, when it comes to the Doctor's companion,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,火炬木的档案就离奇的缺乏\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}the Torchwood files are strangely lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,证据似乎都被毁坏了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It seems the evidence has been corrupted,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,某种叫"恶狼"的病毒\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}something called Bad Wolf virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我们有这些照片\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}At least we've got these photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,它们是第一手资料 埃尔顿\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}They're first-hand evidence. Elton?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对是伦敦口音 她来自伦敦\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It was a London accent, definitely. She's from London.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们到街上找\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So we hit the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就去那儿 四处拍照\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We get out there. We take the photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,某处总会有人知道她是谁\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Someone's got to know who she is somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但伦敦是个很大的地方\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But London's a big place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我很清楚 我女儿就住在那地方\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I should know, my own daughter's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,布里吉 别把这事私人化了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Bridget, don't make this personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢被碰 也不喜欢多愁善感 谢谢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I don't like to be touched literally or metaphorically, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有时间了 抓紧时间 出去\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I haven't got the time. Bleeding hearts, outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,找到那女孩 去\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Find me that girl! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,马上行动\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Now! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然后开始了 不可能任务\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And so it began, the impossible task.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,在街道上四处搜寻\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}To scour the mean streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在大首都中找一个不知名的女孩\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}To search a major capital city for an unknown girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在失去灵魂的沸腾大都市里 穷追直至抓获那副脸孔\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}T 0 hum' down that face in a seething metropolis of lost souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在百万人中寻找那个女孩\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}To find that one girl in ten million.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 那是洛斯·泰勒 就住在那边\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, that's Rose Tyler. She lives just down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,巴克纳尔楼 48号\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Bucknall House, number 48.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,她妈妈是杰琪·泰勒\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Her mother's Jackie Tyler.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一家人都很好 就有一点古怪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Nice family, bit odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ Don't you know it's a beautiful new day ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 杰琪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oi, Jackie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 亲爱的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Hello, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今晚在"旋转独轮"那儿见 好吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'll see you down the Spinning Wheel tonight, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,酒吧竞猜 不醉不归\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Pub quiz. Get them in! All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经训练过了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'd been trained for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多·肯尼迪的课程包含\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Victor Kennedy's classes covered
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,基本监视和间谍活动\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}basic surveillance and espionage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,第一步 锁定你的目标\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Step one, engage your target.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,找些理由和对方交谈\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Find some excuse to start a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但我该怎么做呢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But how was I going to do this? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了 我能和你换一镑零钱吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Excuse me, luv, you couldn't give us a quid for two fifties, could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yeah.just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱 祝福你\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, lovely. Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,第二步 用不惹人起疑的方式\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Step two, without provoking suspicion,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,获得目标的名字\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}get on first-name terms with the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 我叫杰琪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}My name's Jackie, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔顿\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm Elton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,姓埃尔顿的人可不常见\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, you don't meet many Eltons, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 除了你\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Apart from the obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,第三步 用笑话或些幽默策略迎取对方欢心\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Step three, ingratiate yourself with a joke or some humorous device.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.44,0:21:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你 埃尔顿\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I tell you what, Elton.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们本来是两个陌生人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Here we are complete strangers
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我却在向你展示我的内裤\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and I'm flashing you my knickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,第四步 找到某种方法使自己融入目标的家庭\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Step four, find some subtle way to integrate yourself into the target's household.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你 我来这因为我的洗衣机坏了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Mind you, I'm only down here 'cause my washing machine's knackered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.69,0:21:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你懂修理东西 对吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I don't suppose you're any good at fixing things, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这了 保险丝\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Here we are. It was the fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,机器没有问题\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There's nothing wrong with the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 都正常工作了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's fine, all working.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔顿 我可能随时需要你\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, Elton, I should have you on tap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,以前有个小伙子叫米奇 这类事都是他处理的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I used to have this little mate called Mickey, he did all that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他已经走了 保佑他\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}He's gone now, bless him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果需要我 打电话吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Well, if you need me, give us a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你留个号码\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'll jot down my number.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你去写 我给你倒杯茶\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You do that and I'll make us a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,坐一下吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Go on, go and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:21:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,随便看电视\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Put the telly on if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能忍受这种安静\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I can't bear it silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我这些天老是这样 喋喋不休的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's just me these days, rattling about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.13,0:22:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我女儿 但她去旅游了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There's my daughter, but she's gone travelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直保持她房间整洁\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I keep her bedroom all nice and ready though,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,随时准备她回来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}just in case she comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她的名字是\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And her name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,洛斯 很不错的名字\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's a nice name, Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 她去哪旅游了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So, where is she travelling?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,到处跑\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}All over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.87,0:22:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,她带着手机的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She's got her mobile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我偶尔接到她的电话 但是比我想的要少\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I get a call now and then. Not as often as I'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.98,0:22:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管如此 那个年纪 谁愿意费心给家里打电话呢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Still, at that age, who can be bothered phoning home?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她和谁一起 她有同伴吗 还是…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yeah. Who's she with? Is it mates, is it? Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.40,0:22:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就是些同伴\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}just mates, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.72,0:22:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是我 有你这样会泡茶的妈妈\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Well, if I had you making a nice cup of tea like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.54,0:22:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不会远离开家呢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I wouldn't stray far from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:22:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你真可爱\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You're a charmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:22:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,再说一次\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:22:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 我真想亲你一口\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Magnificent! Oh, I could kiss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.81,0:23:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了 我不能 我的痴疹\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Except I can't, of course. The eczeema.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我还用手机拍了一张她的照片\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I've even got a picture of her on my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.13,0:23:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你按照四个步骤准确地完成了任务\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You've achieved steps one to four in precise order.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么做到的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}How did you manage it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.56,0:23:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不容易 她把所有秘密都紧锁于胸\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I had to work very hard. She keeps everything very close to her chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个好胸\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's a hell of a chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.93,0:23:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你怎继续\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But how do you move on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,第五步 那才是重点问题\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Step five, that's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,第五步 这是这周的功课\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Step five. That's this week's homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.18,0:23:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人给我一份详尽的作战计划\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I want a full plan of attack from each of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始 快动起来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Now, go on! Vamoose!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.31,0:23:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,赶快 有很多活要干呢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Avanti! There's work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.14,0:23:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔顿 继续深入\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And, Elton, keep infiltrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.68,0:23:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不惜一切地获取信息 孩子 明白吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You will do anything to get that information, boy, anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.65,0:23:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是 先生\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,布里吉…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh... Oh, Bridget.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.82,0:23:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,布里吉 可以和你单独谈谈吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Bridget? Oh, yes. Could I have a word with you in private, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.64,0:23:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,斯金纳先生要载我一乘\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Mr Skinner's giving me a lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.61,0:23:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以送你回去 斯金纳先生不会介意的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, I can drop you at the station. I'm sure Mr Skinner won't mind, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.33,0:23:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.06,0:23:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,布里吉 下周见\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}All right, Bridget, I'll see you next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.77,0:24:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,斯金纳先生 我不是八卦\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Now, Mr Skinner, I don't mean to pry,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.55,0:24:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但你有没有回吻了布里吉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}but did you give Bridget a little kiss back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.72,0:24:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I think I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.53,0:24:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你方法得当\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And if you get your way,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你们之间会有更多吻的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}might there be more little kisses between the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.80,0:24:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也许会\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I think there might.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.12,0:24:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢肯定  - 真棒\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I knew it! That's brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.75,0:24:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,现在别激动的太早 慢慢来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Now, let's not get excited. We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.55,0:24:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,潜伏工作进行地很好\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Infiltration went well
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.16,0:24:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,因为杰琪老是打电话过来 需要这需要那\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'cause Jackie kept phoning up, needing this and needing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.59,0:24:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪 她需要做的事怎么这么多\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It was strange, the amount of things that needed doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.50,0:24:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就像她公寓被诅咒了一样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's like that flat was jinxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.64,0:24:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪 这些保险丝老是烧断\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's weird, these fuses, they keep on blowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.85,0:24:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,附近一定有个变电站\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You must be near a substation
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.91,0:24:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你总遇到电力高峰\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'cause then you get the power surges.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.36,0:24:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了 修好了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Still, there we go. Fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.05,0:25:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,来 给我最喜欢的助手一点小奖励\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Here we are. A little reward for my favourite handyman.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.40,0:25:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的不能这样 外面有车在等着我呢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I shouldn't really, I've got the car outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.45,0:25:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以随时打出租车啊\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You could always splash out on a taxi,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.06,0:25:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,或者…别的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.41,0:25:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,看看会有什么结果\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}See what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.60,0:25:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.54,0:25:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,干杯\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.36,0:25:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,干杯\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.97,0:25:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,味道很好\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.39,0:25:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么 法国的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What's that, French?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.96,0:25:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是 那些法国人真懂得做这些\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I suppose so. They know how to do things, the French.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.93,0:25:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是洛斯给你的吗 我是说 她在法国吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Is it from Rose? I mean, is she in France?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.68,0:25:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我女儿今晚不会回来 以防你想知道的话\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}My daughter won't be coming back tonight, just in case you're wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.57,0:25:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这里完全属于我们\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We've got the place to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.64,0:25:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.16,0:25:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,音乐很好听\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Nice music.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.81,0:25:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"美声男伶"组合\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Il Divo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.22,0:25:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.62,0:25:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚说\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You were saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.60,0:25:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,电力高峰\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Power surges.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.80,0:25:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,变电站造成的 没错\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}From the substation, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.80,0:25:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,它也把这里变热了吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Is that why it gets so hot in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.47,0:25:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,很热吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Is it hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.25,0:25:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我想是的 你应该把夹克脱掉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, I think so. You should take your jacket off.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.86,0:25:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我很好\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.72,0:26:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你 都要沸腾了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, look, you must be boiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.40,0:26:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你的衬衫\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, look at your shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.73,0:26:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,被我弄脏了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I've ruined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.28,0:26:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不 说真的 还好\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, honestly, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.21,0:26:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,把它脱掉 我把它拿去洗了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Take it off, I'll put it in the wash.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.42,0:26:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 只是一小滴\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, come on, it's only a little drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.35,0:26:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,现在呢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.10,0:26:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,全毁了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.43,0:26:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我就到了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And there I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.13,0:26:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,终极第五步\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}the ultimate step five.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.05,0:26:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,最完美地渗透\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The perfect infiltration.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.96,0:26:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,目标 杰琪·泰勒\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Target, Jackie Tyler. Atta boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.37,0:26:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你是对的 确实有点热\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You're right, it is a bit hot,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.06,0:26:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,而且越来越热\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}but it's about to get hotter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.48,0:26:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一会见\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.49,0:26:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 小心点 再见\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}All right, be careful. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.90,0:26:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.38,0:26:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是我女儿\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That was my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.99,0:26:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你 对不起\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, look at you. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.03,0:26:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是有点犯傻\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I was just being stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.14,0:26:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她还好吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.39,0:26:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她离我很远\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She's so far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.97,0:27:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有时我被遗弃在这…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I get left here sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.24,0:27:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道她去哪了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and I don't know where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.34,0:27:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,任何事都有可能在她身上发生 任何事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Anything could be happening to her, anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.02,0:27:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是有点神经错乱\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And I just go a bit mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.56,0:27:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,穿上你的衬衫\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, put your shirt back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.14,0:27:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她在哪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.74,0:27:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不重要\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.24,0:27:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.82,0:27:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好走吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.93,0:27:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,其实…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.10,0:27:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那时我突然想到\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And that's when it struck me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.28,0:27:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,脱衬衫时总会想些奇奇怪怪的事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Funny the things you think of with your shirt off.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.46,0:27:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但那时 我意识到了什么才是真正重要的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But that's when I realised what was really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.74,0:27:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,别再管洛斯了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Never mind about Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.77,0:27:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至不会去问\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm not even gonna ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.84,0:27:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把衣服穿上\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And I will put my shirt back on
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.41,0:27:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我要出去给我们买个批萨\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}because I'm gonna go out and get us both a pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.51,0:27:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我想你需要高兴一下\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'Cause I reckon you need cheering up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.85,0:27:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她出去漂游了 谁留下来来照顾你\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She goes swanning off and who's left to care about you, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.03,0:28:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我说不如点一份美味的批萨\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So I say, nice bit of pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.57,0:28:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把电视打开到很大声\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We'll put the telly on nice and loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.47,0:28:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,把隔壁的女人吵到不得安宁\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}we'll annoy that woman next door,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.12,0:28:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就我们两个 最佳搭档 好吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}just you and me, as proper mates. Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.82,0:28:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,伙伴 来吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Mates. Go on,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.28,0:28:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,答应吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.85,0:28:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.93,0:28:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,突然之间 很多事情变的有意义\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}All of a sudden, a lot of things made sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.44,0:28:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直迷失在阴谋和外星人和目标里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'd got so lost in conspiracies and aliens and targets,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.72,0:28:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,却一直错过眼前的东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'd been missing the obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.64,0:28:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的喜欢杰琪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'Cause I did like Jackie,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.53,0:28:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但我更喜欢另一个人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}but I liked someone else even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.52,0:28:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ Hey you with the pretty face ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.02,0:28:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ Welcome to the human race ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.78,0:28:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ A celebration Mr Blue Sky's up there waiting ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.78,0:28:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ And today is the day we've waited for ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.06,0:28:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ Oh ho-ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.68,0:28:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ Mr Blue Sky, please tell us why… ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.89,0:29:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我们进去吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Right. Let's get inside, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.59,0:29:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,批萨要冷了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The pizza's getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.12,0:29:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我翻了你的大衣\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I went in your coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.76,0:29:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我人生第一次想到 "我来付钱"\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}For once in my life I thought, "I'll pay."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.05,0:29:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 他是个好男人 他不会接受任何东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I thought, "He's such a nice man, "he won't accept anything
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.76,0:29:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我把十元钱塞进他的口袋\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}so I'll just slip a tenner in his pocket."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.37,0:29:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我发现了什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And look what I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.64,0:29:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我女儿的照片\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}A photograph of my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.80,0:29:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不 不是你想的那样 我能解释\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, no, no. It's not like that. I can explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.07,0:29:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你当然会\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I bet you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.84,0:29:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是什么不正当的人 我没在追求她\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I wasn't being pervy or anything. I wasn't after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.68,0:29:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我在找博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I was looking for the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.04,0:29:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.85,0:29:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我想明白了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I worked that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.71,0:29:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,从来都和我无关 是吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'Cause it's never me, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.14,0:29:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不 一开始是那样的 但后来我改变心意了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, but that's how it started, but I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.22,0:29:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,让我跟你说说那些被抛弃的人的故事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Let me tell you something. About those who get left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.51,0:29:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那很艰苦\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Because it's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.38,0:29:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你最后也会变成这样 很艰苦\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And that's what you become, hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.07,0:29:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果说我学会了什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But if there's one thing I've learnt,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.20,0:29:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是我永远不会让她失望\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}it's that I will never let her down
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.44,0:29:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我这辈子都会保护他俩\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and I'll protect them both until the end of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.00,0:29:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不论你想要什么 我警告你\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So whatever you want, I'm warning you,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.09,0:29:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,休想得逞\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.12,0:29:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但杰琪 我只是想见见他\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But, Jackie, I only wanted to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.65,0:30:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为你喜欢我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I thought you liked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.91,0:30:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.72,0:30:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧滚开这里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Just get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.05,0:30:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我说滚\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I said get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.96,0:30:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,让我静一静\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.23,0:30:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她是对的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.28,0:30:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这真可耻 我们利用了那个女人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's shameful. We used that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.20,0:30:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道不能相信你\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I knew I couldn't trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.90,0:30:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个冒失鬼\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You broke cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.05,0:30:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个笨蛋 你败在了第五步\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You stupid little man, you failed step five.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.42,0:30:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎第五步\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I don't care about step five!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.12,0:30:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,自从你出现后一切都变味了 肯尼迪先生\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'Cause it's all gone wrong, Mr Kennedy, ever since you turned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.68,0:30:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们以前来这儿 每周欢聚\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We used to come here every week and we'd have a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.65,0:30:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是朋友\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.18,0:30:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,难怪他们不来了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No wonder they stopped coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.02,0:30:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,布丽斯再也没来过\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I mean, there's no Bliss anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.37,0:30:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还有布里吉 她再没有再出现过\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and even Bridget, she hasn't turned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.19,0:30:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直打电话给她 但没有回复\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I've been phoning and phoning, there's no reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.32,0:30:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,谁能怪她\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Who can blame her?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.22,0:30:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 维克多\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm sorry, Victor,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.74,0:30:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在你靠自己吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}but you're on your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.22,0:30:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我要退出\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'cause I am leaving
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.40,0:30:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是 斯金纳先生\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and so are you, Mr Skinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.69,0:30:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,至于你 厄什拉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And as for you, Ursula,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.62,0:30:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你要跟我来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}you're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.97,0:31:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去金蝉饭店 我们去吃中餐\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And we're going to the Golden Locust and we're gonna have a Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.05,0:31:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这和那有什么关系\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What's that got to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.54,0:31:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 你和我 在一起\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I mean, you and me. Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.39,0:31:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,吃个饭\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Having a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.71,0:31:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你愿意\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}If you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.59,0:31:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常乐意\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, I'd love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.88,0:31:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不能走\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But you can't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.68,0:31:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你们永远不知道他在哪里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But you can't leave. You'll never know what he was doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.43,0:31:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远不会知道许多年前 博士为什么在你家\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}the Doctor. You'll never know what he was doing in your house all those years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.58,0:31:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远都不想知道\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, I'll never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.37,0:31:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,厄什拉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Ursula,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.20,0:31:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,拿上你的东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}get your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.36,0:31:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,斯金纳先生 你来吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Mr Skinner, are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.66,0:31:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不是去吃中国餐 如果你不介意 只是走走\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Not to the Chinese if you don't mind. just sort of walking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.53,0:31:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然愿意\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I certainly am.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.88,0:31:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Victor,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.61,0:31:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你好运吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.32,0:31:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.95,0:31:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,斯金纳先生\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Mr Skinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.51,0:31:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,请问你可以待一会吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}would you stay for a minute, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.52,0:31:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要出去\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We're walking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.42,0:31:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我有布里吉的电话\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I've got numbers for Bridget.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.29,0:31:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我有纪录 我有她的旧号码\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I've kept records. I've got old numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.10,0:31:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以找到她 你和我一起\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We could track her down together, you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.19,0:32:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这才像老队伍的精神\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's more like the old team spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.87,0:32:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩过的愉快\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You two have a nice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.18,0:32:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你能找到她\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I hope you find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.82,0:32:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我会给你发邮件\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'll email you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.18,0:32:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,再靠近一点点\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Just come a little closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.02,0:32:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我想吃对虾\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I love prawns.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.97,0:32:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,香酥脆皮鸭 你呢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Crispy aromatic duck. Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.52,0:32:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘拿手机了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, I left my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.33,0:32:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真的  - 对 不在我口袋里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Really? Yeah. It's not in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.49,0:32:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,咱愤然退出的气势都没了是吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So much for the big exit. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.79,0:32:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 快点\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Come on, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.47,0:32:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是反悔 我只是落下了我的…电话\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm not stopping, I just left my...phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.18,0:32:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Victor?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.14,0:32:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,拿上你的电话然后离开\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Take your phone and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.49,0:32:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,斯金纳先生在哪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Where's Mr Skinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.60,0:32:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他去厕所了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}He's gone to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.65,0:32:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但这里没有厕所\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But we haven't got toilets,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.91,0:32:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都只能用拐角处的酒吧里的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}we have to use the pub on the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.81,0:32:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那他就在那里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Well, that's where he is, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.76,0:32:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.92,0:33:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,什么声音\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.85,0:33:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 没什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It was nothing. It was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.56,0:33:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.47,0:33:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.72,0:33:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那是斯金纳先生\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's Mr Skinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.51,0:33:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,维克多 看看你的手\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Victor, look at your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.35,0:33:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我的其他部分\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Look at the rest of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.43,0:33:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你们对外星人有所涉猎\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You've dabbled with aliens,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.59,0:33:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,现在看看真正的外星人吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}now meet the genuine article.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.89,0:33:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天哪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.01,0:33:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You're a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.68,0:33:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.74,0:33:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,一个东西\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}A thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.96,0:33:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的真身\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}This thing is my true form.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.98,0:33:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,比你们那粗糙 粉红的躯体好多了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Better than that crude pink shape you call a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.26,0:33:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了 我在哪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What happened? Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.23,0:33:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,厄什拉 是你吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Ursula, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.01,0:33:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是斯金纳先生\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's Mr Skinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.37,0:33:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你对他做了什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What have you done to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.04,0:33:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我吸收了他\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I've absorbed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.87,0:33:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,科林 是你吗 科林\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Colin? Is that you? Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.63,0:33:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,布里吉 亲爱的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Bridget, my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.52,0:33:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天哪 那是布里吉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, my God! That's Bridget.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.33,0:33:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,科林 你在哪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Colin, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.74,0:33:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这 布里吉 我很好\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm here, Bridget. It's all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.90,0:33:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我被困住了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm close.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.85,0:33:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你把他们俩都吸收了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You've absorbed them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.93,0:34:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,布丽斯呢 她在哪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What about Bliss? Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.98,0:34:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.46,0:34:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你们不会想知道的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I said you really don't want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.02,0:34:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你把他们都吸收了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You've absorbed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.25,0:34:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你是某种…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You're some sort of
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.26,0:34:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,吸收兽\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}absorbathon!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.20,0:34:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,吸收怪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}An absorbaling.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.03,0:34:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,吸收人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}An Abzorbaloff.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.50,0:34:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不错 我喜欢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yes, I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.14,0:34:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,放他们走\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Let them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.42,0:34:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我命令你\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm ordering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.23,0:34:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,放了他们\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Let those people go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.12,0:34:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们的味道很好\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, but they taste so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.04,0:34:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,想想博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Just think about the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.81,0:34:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他尝起来会怎样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Ooh, how will he taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.07,0:34:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那些经历 那些知识\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}All that experience, all that knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.30,0:34:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就算要我吸收杰琪·泰勒 那也值了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And if I've got to absorb Jackie Tyler to get to him, then so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.38,0:34:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Don't you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.56,0:34:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们走 我打也要把他们打出来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}If I have to beat them out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.40,0:34:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 请别打我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh! Oh! No, no, please don't hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.82,0:34:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我 我只是一只迟钝笨拙的野兽\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Look at me, I'm such a slow and clumsy beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.59,0:34:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,请别打我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Please don't hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.33,0:34:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那把他们还给我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Well, then. Give them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.92,0:35:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 你说像这样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What, you mean like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.16,0:35:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只要碰一下 就这么简单\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Just one touch! That's all it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.17,0:35:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.72,0:35:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,放开她\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Leave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.57,0:35:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.27,0:35:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔顿 对不起\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, Elton. I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.33,0:35:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能碰我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}you can't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.68,0:35:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,厄什拉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Ursula.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.51,0:35:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,确实很有抵抗性\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Most likely to fight back indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.58,0:35:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,放开她\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Leave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.17,0:35:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.99,0:35:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这不公平\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No, that's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.42,0:35:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她的味道像小鸡\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}She tastes like chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.25,0:35:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔顿 你在哪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Elton, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.29,0:35:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.94,0:35:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,肯尼迪先生 拜托了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Mr Kennedy, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.50,0:35:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我在请求您\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm asking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.82,0:36:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我在乞求您\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm begging you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.30,0:36:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,把她还给我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}give her back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.51,0:36:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.41,0:36:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一旦被吸收 这个过程无法逆转\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Once they've been absorbed, the process is irreversible.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.11,0:36:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.33,0:36:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我被吸收了 我可以读到它的思想\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Now I've been absorbed, I can read his thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.29,0:36:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, my God! Elton,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.90,0:36:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是下一个 快走\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}you're next. Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.20,0:36:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见他了 他不会让你走的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Now you've seen him, he can't let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.46,0:36:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Just run.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.74,0:36:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 别管我 快走\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Go on, never mind me. Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.17,0:36:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她真聪明\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Isn't she the clever one?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.02,0:36:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑 埃尔顿\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Run, Elton!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.37,0:36:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,跑\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.27,0:36:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,保护好自己 孩子\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Save yourself, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.36,0:36:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,拼命跑\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Run for your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.04,0:37:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.83,0:37:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这么快就放弃了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Have you given up so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.67,0:37:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么意义\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.02,0:37:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我能去哪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Where would I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.00,0:37:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要的一切…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Everything I ever wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.84,0:37:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,都被吸收了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Has been absorbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.56,0:37:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔顿 别这么说\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, Elton. Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.04,0:37:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是真的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.71,0:37:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那加入我们 加入我们 小伙子\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Then join us.join us, little man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.17,0:37:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 这里有永恒的平静\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Come on. It's everlasting peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.77,0:37:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 加入我们\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Come on, join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.62,0:37:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,和我溶为一体\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Dissolve into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.66,0:37:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有人想跟你说句话\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Someone wants a word with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.72,0:37:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你伤了我妈妈的心了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You upset my mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.07,0:38:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一大个外星吸收怪在这里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}A great big absorbing creature from outer space
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.98,0:38:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你还急着找我算账\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and you're having a go at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.10,0:38:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人能让我妈妈伤心\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No one upsets my mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.30,0:38:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,终于\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}At last.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.40,0:38:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,终极大餐 博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The greatest feast of all, the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.53,0:38:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.72,0:38:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,某种吸收矩阵\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}A sort of absorbatrix...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.28,0:38:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,吸收隆…吸收人…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Absorbaklon... Abzorbaloff...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.88,0:38:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,吸收人 对\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Abzorbaloff, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.02,0:38:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我觉得吗 他是不是有点像斯利辛\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Is it me or is he a bit Slitheen?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.63,0:38:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是来自拉克斯科瑞法洛托瑞斯星球\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Not from Rexicoricophalvitorius, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.58,0:38:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我才不是那群猪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No. I'm not that swine!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.45,0:38:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我鄙视他们 我来自他们的姊妹星\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I spit on them! I was born on their twin planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.64,0:38:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗 拉克斯科瑞法洛托瑞斯星的姊妹星是什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Really? What's the twin planet of Rexicoricophalvitorius?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.07,0:38:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛星\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Clom. Clom?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.87,0:38:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛星 对 一旦我拿到你的旅行机器 我就大胜而归\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Clom. Yes, and I'll return there victorious, once I possess your travelling machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.28,0:38:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那永远不会发生\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Well, that's never gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.64,0:38:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,会的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.88,0:38:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你会向我投降 博士 否则这个人就得死\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You'll surrender yourself to me, Doctor, or this one dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.39,0:38:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗 我读过你很多资料 博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You see, I've read about you, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.41,0:38:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我研究过你 充满热情\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I've studied you. So passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.20,0:38:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那么讨人喜欢 你不会让无辜的人死\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So sweet. You wouldn't let an innocent man die.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.67,0:38:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你投降 否则我就吸收掉他\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And I'll absorb him unless you give yourself to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.37,0:39:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,讨人喜欢 或许吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Sweet, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.67,0:39:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,充满热情 应该是吧 但不要和友好弄混了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Passionate, I suppose. But don't ever mistake that for nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.13,0:39:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你随便吧\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.01,0:39:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他会死的 博士\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}He'll die, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.78,0:39:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Go on, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.40,0:39:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,吸收\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.97,0:39:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,提醒你 其他人可能有话要说\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Mind you, the others might have something to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.48,0:39:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Others?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.18,0:39:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他是对的 博士是对的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}He's right! The Doctor's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.00,0:39:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能让它得逞\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We can't let him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.62,0:39:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,斯金纳先生 布里吉 拉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, Mr Skinner. Bridget, pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.67,0:39:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看在上帝的份上 拉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}For God's sake, pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.55,0:39:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就算这是我们最后能做的一件事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}If it's the last thing we ever do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.88,0:39:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,布丽斯 我们大家一起\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Bliss! All of us, together,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.43,0:39:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 用力拉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}come on! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.53,0:39:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,LINDA 联合起来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}LINDA united!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.08,0:39:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,拉…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.08,0:39:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔顿 手杖 弄断它\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Elton! The cane, break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.89,0:39:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手杖\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}My cane!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.27,0:39:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个蠢货\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You stupid man!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.15,0:40:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.14,0:40:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了什么\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.48,0:40:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,手杖创造了一个限制场\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The cane created a limitation field.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.76,0:40:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,现在坏了 他停不下来了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Now it's broken, he can't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.97,0:40:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这个吸收者正在被吸收\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}The absorber is being absorbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.73,0:40:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,被什么吸收\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}By What?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.45,0:40:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,被地球\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}By the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.49,0:40:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 埃尔顿\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Bye-bye, Elton.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.36,0:40:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.50,0:40:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她是谁\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Who was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.48,0:40:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,厄什拉\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That was Ursula.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.24,0:41:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.28,0:41:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多是\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.21,0:41:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因为博士还有别的要说\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Because the Doctor still had more to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.80,0:41:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得了 对吗\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You don't remember, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.46,0:41:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他解释了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And then he explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.39,0:41:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那晚 许多年前…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That night, all those years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.98,0:41:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你的房子里有个影子\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There was a shadow in your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.09,0:41:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗中的一个活影子\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}A living shadow in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.04,0:41:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一片元素之影从"呼啸宅"里逃脱了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}An elemental shade that had escaped from the Howling Halls.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.05,0:41:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我阻止了它 但…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I stopped it, but
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.93,0:41:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我来不及救她\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I wasn't in time to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.48,0:41:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.15,0:41:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那晚我妈妈死了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Because that was the night my mother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.04,0:42:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们忘记是因为必须忘记\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We forget because we must.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.06,0:42:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 你看到了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}So, there you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.18,0:42:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我经历的最可怕的事情\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Turns out I've had the most terrible things happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.01,0:42:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,和最美好的回忆\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and the most brilliant things,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.30,0:42:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而且有时 我也分不清它们的区别\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and sometimes, well, I can't tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.30,0:42:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都是同一件事 只不过是我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}They're all the same thing. They're just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.39,0:43:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 斯蒂芬·金说过\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}You know, Stephen King said once, he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.64,0:43:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救和诅咒是一样的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}"Salvation and damnation are the same thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.08,0:43:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我从不理解这句话的意思\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And I never knew what he meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.60,0:43:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我知道了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But I do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.50,0:43:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,因为博士可能很伟大 但回过头来想想\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'Cause the Doctor might be wonderful, but thinking back,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.66,0:43:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我有这么特殊的经历\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I was having such a special time,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.74,0:43:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,只一点点 我有过这么美好的小社团\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}just for a bit. I had this nice little gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.24,0:43:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs14}♪ I'll tell you once more,before I get off the floor… ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.09,0:43:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而他们被摧毁了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And they were destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.93,0:43:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不是他的错\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's not his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.89,0:43:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这就是碰到博士会发生的事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But maybe that's what happens if you touch the Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.62,0:43:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕只有一瞬间\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}even for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.41,0:43:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想洛斯和杰琪\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I keep thinking of Rose and Jackie,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.50,0:43:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她们还要为此付出多少代价\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and how much longer before they pay the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.62,0:43:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还是不要那么悲伤了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, now don't get all miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.08,0:43:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,振作起来 埃尔顿 你还有我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Come on, Elton. You've still got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.90,0:43:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.06,0:43:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,博士说他可以用他的魔棒做最后一件事\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}'Cause the Doctor said he could do one last thing with his magic wand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.16,0:44:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我可以钻进这个吸收矩阵 分离出最后的受害人…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}If I can key into the absorption matrix and separate the last victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.86,0:44:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,全部重建太迟了 但是…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's too late for total reconstruction, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.99,0:44:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,埃尔顿 拿个铁锹过来\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Elton! Fetch a spade!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.12,0:44:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管那样 在那一切发生之后\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Even then, after all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.53,0:44:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,博士最后一次拯救了我\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}the Doctor saved me one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.90,0:44:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,她就在这\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Here she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.01,0:44:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可能比这更糟\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Could be worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.08,0:44:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我不会变老\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}At least I'll never age.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.14,0:44:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,而且真的很平静 超出你的想象\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And it really is quite peaceful. You'd be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.49,0:44:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一段奇特的关系\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's a relationship of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.99,0:44:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们成功了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But we manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.88,0:44:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们甚至有了点爱情生活\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}We've even got a bit of a love life.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.64,0:44:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是不要深入这话题了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}Oh, let's not go into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.57,0:44:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管别人怎么想\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And I don't care what anyone thinks,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.32,0:44:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱她\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.45,0:44:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但重要的是\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.58,0:44:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我最后还是买了个缩放遥控\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}There you are, I even bought a remote zoom.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.60,0:45:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但我要说的是\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But what I wanted to say is,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.17,0:45:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 当你还是个孩子的时候\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}you know, when you're a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.37,0:45:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,人们告诉你生活只是 长大 工作\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}they tell you that it's all grow up, get a job,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.80,0:45:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,结婚 买房 生子 就是这样\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}get married, get a house, have a kid and that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.42,0:45:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.75,0:45:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真相是 世界比那更不同寻常…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}But the truth is, the world is so much stranger than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.78,0:45:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,更黑暗…\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}It's so much darker
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.52,0:45:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,更疯狂\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}and so much madder.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.49,0:45:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,更精彩\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}And so much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.07,0:45:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,第三十届奥林匹克\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}30th Olympiad.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.35,0:45:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.98,0:45:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不安全\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}They're not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.14,0:45:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在花园里\N{\b0\fs14\3c&H202020}They're in the garden.
